nodes.text: Syphacc's Bountiful Bounties was an organization that provided bounties to bounty hunters in exchange for credits, operated by the cyborg Syphacc. After Nakano Lash, a former bounty hunter who had disappeared after betraying several other hunters during a job, resurfaced, Syphacc attempted to contact a number of the hunters she had betrayed, including Beilert Valance and Boba Fett.
